	<term>Background <emphasis remap='I'>"name" filename</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Change Background image to specified file</para>
		<para>Copies image file specified by filename into user's non-configurable directory. 
Depending on Background configuration in look file, this may not have any effect.
</para>
